About Us - Brighton Jones                     Brighton Jones  menu     Money in and of itself is not what motivates us.  It’s about helping people navigate the complexities that come with having it. For us, that boils down to understanding in detail the values, goals and personal circumstances of each of our clients.We knew from the beginning that there was a better way, and we set out to build a firm that set a new standard for wealth management. Instead of focusing on one narrow slice, such as investments, we took a broader approach, one in which a team of individuals collaborate across a client’s entire balance sheet. From investments to long-term strategy to tax and estate planning, our clients have access to the expertise they need when they need it.Our team shares the same philosophy and goals in serving our clients – and working together in the same office improves the quality of our process and the recommendations that we make. Planning decisions don’t get made in a vacuum, the strategy is understandable, and the ongoing execution is handled in a way that ensures nothing falls through the cracks. In the end, the entire client experience is elevated.We also wanted to eliminate any conflicts of interest. While our legal status as a fiduciary requires us to put our clients’ interests ahead of our own, our fee-only compensation structure underlines that commitment. It eliminates the bias that can arise when a firm is paid commissions or backend fees that come with recommending or selling products.In the end, it’s about creating true partnerships that thrive on transparency, accountability, and collaboration. Supporting every client in the pursuit of their goals, using our expertise to help them live their version of a richer life.    OUR SERVICES Let’s TalkWhether you have a specific question, or you’re interested in learning more about how our approach could be tailored to your situation, we’d be happy to hear from you. Please feel free to be in touch in whatever way works best for you. meet our team     
Comprehensive Wealth & Financial Management Takes a Team Approach                     Brighton Jones  menu      The smartest person in the room is sometimes a group of people.We knew from the start that it would take a team approach to deliver the kinds of financial services and advice we would choose for ourselves.Truly world-class wealth management services as we envision them should be just as dynamic as the world we live in. To us this means bringing well-informed experts to the table to share their unique perspectives, each committed to helping you achieve your goals.This team—your team—develops a personalized strategic plan that takes into account how decisions in one area of your finances impact the bigger picture. So not only do you get the benefit of some very smart people working together to get you where you want to go, you no longer need to wrangle a loose group of unrelated advisors with differing agendas.From short- and long-term strategies that take into account all aspects of your financial life; to investment advice that’s objective and tailored to your personal situation; to estate & tax planning strategies that are proactive, efficient and accountable; everything we do is centered around you.   OUR SERVICES Related Insights Portfolio Diversification Helping clients obtain peace of mind for long-term goalsOur own Charles Brighton discusses our “cash needs analysis” strategy in the Wal read more Common Client Questions Managing money concepts – how do we teach our kids?The school year has nearly ended, or may already have ended for your children. read more Investment Advisory Can your portfolio help make a positive impact in the world?Can your investments do more than provide for your retirement? Is it possible to mak read more See ALL Let’s TalkWhether you have a specific question, or you’re interested in learning more about how our approach could be tailored to your situation, we’d be happy to hear from you. Please feel free to be in touch in whichever way works best for you. meet our team     
Available Opportunities - Brighton Jones                     Brighton Jones  menu     Available Opportunities  + Join us So you’ve updated your LinkedIn, lined up your references, and decided to apply for a position at Brighton Jones. What’s next?Our hiring process is designed to do more than identify the right skills and professionalism, though it’s really good at that too. What we’re looking for is the right people. Because at the end of the day, that’s really what we offer our clients.What can you expect?Take a look at the available opportunities below. Submit your resume and cover letter, and be sure to highlight your unique qualities and the reasons you’re interested in working with us.Do you have something you want to tell us in addition to what’s on your resume? We want to hear about it!  Click here to submit a short video to tell us more about you.We’ll give you a call to talk about the position and determine next steps. When you come in to our offices, you’ll have the chance to meet potential team members, ask all your questions, and learn more about Brighton Jones, job responsibilities, and our culture.It’s a process that takes some time, but if this is the right opportunity for you, it’s worth it for both of us—we certainly want to get to know you, but it’s also important that you get to know Brighton Jones. View available opportunities.   Let’s TalkWe’re always on the lookout for passionate people whose interests and skills match our needs. If what you’ve read here intrigues you, we’d be happy to hear from you. contact us     
