Company Overview of Brighton Jones, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Brighton Jones, LLC, a wealth management company, provides financial advisory services for individuals and families with substantial wealth and assets in Washington, California, and Arizona. It offers objective advice and analysis services in the areas of investment, estate, tax, cash management, and overall life planning. The company provides private client, family wealth management, shared family office, and tax planning and compliance services. Brighton Jones, LLC was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Seattle, Washington with an additional office in Scottsdale, Arizona.


506 Second AvenueSuite 1800Seattle, WA 98104United StatesFounded in 1999



Phone: 206-329-5546

Fax: 206-329-8843

